      "span_text": "Figure 1A and 1B show that ghrelin has no effect on locomotor activity or rearing in the open field test (locomotor activity: F [CITATION_1] 37) = 0.3659, p = 0.83; rearing:F (4, 37) = 0.4632, p = 0.76).",
